account.descriptionLink:
This is an non-binding opinion poll for current MCAPS holders regarding the fate of the bonding curve pool.

If this vote passes, it will demonstrate that MCAPS holders want the original bonding curve pool at https://initialcapoffering.com/ to be closed, and the remaining MCAPS and USDC assets transferred to token accounts controlled by this DAO.
account.name: Advisory: Close bonding curve pool and transfer assets to the DAO
